      Classes in uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.tuple that implement Tuple 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ArrayTuple
      An ArrayTuple is a simple implementation of the Tuple interface, backed by an array of Objects, referenced by their index.
      class  MapTuple<R>
      A MapTuple is an implementation of Tuple backed by a Map.
      class  ReferenceArrayTuple<R> 
      class  ReflectiveTuple
      A ReflectiveTuple is a Tuple that wraps an object and treats it as a Tuple by using reflection to call fields directly or via getters.
